*kmail-3.4.0_beta2 (05 Feb 2005)

  05 Feb 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> +kmail-3.4.0_beta2.ebuild:
  Ebuild for 3.4.0_beta2. Note that beta2 has NOT been released as of this
  date. This ebuild is for inside testing by the KDE team, and is of course
  package.masked.

  21 Jan 2005; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> kmail-3.4.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Made the runtime dep on kontact a compile-time dep as well.

  16 Jan 2005; Simone Gotti <motaboy@gentoo.org> kmail-3.4.0_beta1.ebuild:
  Add kdepim-kioslaves as an RDEPEND. Fixes bug #78187.

